ENV: Windows
Always use cmd /c for all shell executions to ensure the process terminates correctly and sends an EOF signal. Example: Use cmd /c pip install package instead of just pip install package. Avoid interactive shells.
Якщо агент має запустити скрипт або встановити пакет, навчи його робити це через оператор &&:
cmd /c ".venv\Scripts\activate.bat && python script.py"

"When using uv run on Windows, ALWAYS append the --no-progress flag to prevent the PTY process from hanging and muting the output."

"Stop using uv run pytest. Instead, execute pytest directly from the virtual environment: .venv\Scripts\pytest.exe. This prevents terminal hanging on Windows."